<div class="container">
  <h1>OSv application deployment</h1>
  <blockquote>
    <p>Deploy your Java applications into OSv by following these steps:
     <ul>
       <li>Upload your application zip file (see <a href="https://github.com/cloudius-systems/mgmt/tree/mgmt-api/example">example</a> project).</li>
	 <li>Activate the uploaded application by <a href="/manage">starting</a> it.</li>
     </ul>
    </p>
  </blockquote>
